Instruction.

Required dependecies to install:
$ sudo apt-get install g++
$ sudo apt-get install libglfw3-dev libglu1-mesa-dev
$ sudo apt-get install libglu1-mesa-dev
$ sudo apt-get install libglew-dev
$ sudo apt-get install g++-mingw-w64-i686
$ sudo apt-get install g++-mingw-w64-x86-64


A) General build commnads:
 $ make clean
 $ make

B) Possible build targets:

1. linux
 $ make -C linux

2. x32
 $ make -C x32

3. x64
 $ make -C x64

